io.konik.zugferd.entity

Class Trade

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.konik.zugferd.entity.Trade

  • public class Trade
extends Object
    The Class Trade.
    Groups the various aspects a invoice trade transaction.
    The Trade Transaction is divided into the "global" trade agreements, delivery and trade settlement parameters that can be overwritten/complemented on item basis.
